idea-plugin.description:
    ArcTestDox creates simple documentation from the method names in JUnit test cases.<br/>
For Example, a test class (`FooTests.java`):<br/>
<code>
public class FooTests {
    public void testIsASingleton() {
    }

    public void testAReallyLongNameIsAGoodThing() {
    }

    public void shouldTestSomethingUseful() {
    }
}
</code>

would generate the following :<br/>
<code>
# Tests Found:

##  FooTests
   * is a singleton
   * a really long name is a good thing
   * test something useful
</code>
